Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.67,0:00:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know if we'd be on the same team.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the clumsy one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I must protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane is such a gentle person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see if he is qualified
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to be in a relationship with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is proof that you're my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, she is a little vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She really is a great sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You must cherish your bond with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:00:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have anyone you treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But those two aren't as gentle as her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, one of them is gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But the other one...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he not a gentle person?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.21,0:01:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because he once told me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,a person like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.88,0:01:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he say about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.54,0:01:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird, I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Behave and come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.13,0:01:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Felling of tiredness is losing yourself♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫How do you still create a relationship each other♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It’s my awkward friend’s fault♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Until death, wanting someone somewhere to embrace me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫While the devil is not here and between the chaos♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.96,0:02:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Aiming between win and lose♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.29,0:02:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Not to be running out of patience for now\NI’m trying to be careful♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You'll see I'm always on your side♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and your roller\Ncoaster inside the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The grungy days and the unprecedented catastrophy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Where is the glory buried♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The lonely monster in a moment♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun goes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:03:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫To pierce with the theory♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I tried hard to connect today as well♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The bullet shot by the machinegun goes parallelly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It’s the same today\NTo connect vividly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,♫You’re frigid and the theory in the brain♫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,NAOMI AND ALICE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.00,0:03:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't understand why they are\Ntransporting Others created from humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is Major General Fubuki's order,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,there must be a reason behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If and only if that order came\Nfrom Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it behind this door?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.88,0:04:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.92,0:04:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Communication has been cut off\Nin this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,LOCKED
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,UNLOCKED
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, there is no one inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.04,0:04:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the inside of Arahabaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems different from the time\Nwhen I was an intern.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.04,0:04:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Arahabaki is several floors below Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What you saw, Hanabi, was probably\Nthe upper areas known to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is the secure site\Nthat controls Arahabaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about earlier. You used up too much energy\Nto get us here just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We were being pursued by troops just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.96,0:05:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the only way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,-My head doesn't hurt now.\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.96,0:05:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean what the Chief said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never got into a serious argument\Nwith my brother until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.88,0:05:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was a little concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:06:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother decided to take over my father's work\Nsince he was a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm nothing like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother acted on his own belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And that makes his actions\Neven more unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you are brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's actually harder for brothers\Nto understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother's decisions always confuse me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Major General Karen is\Neven more unpredictable than my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.92,0:06:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, can you spot the access point\Nwithin Arahabaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is too huge,\NI can't get a clear view.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.54,0:06:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is a location\Nwhere the routes converge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's where we must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these all of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.17,0:07:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact Chief Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, there is nothing to be feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I no longer feel fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.33,0:07:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane Randall?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.58,0:07:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your motive of doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We are carrying out our order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We transported them here to make\Nfinal adjustments to our Other weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps our superior thinks it's time\Nto finally put these to practical uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You plan to use my sister as a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:08:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We are in charge of the research facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We take orders from Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But Fubuki is nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Fubuki has\Nother important matters to see to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I find it hard to believe\NFubuki would give such order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.96,0:08:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry, I will keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you need to run now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,These people are lying to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I just overheard them talking about\Ncontacting Chief Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They aren't following orders\Nfrom Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They are working for Chief Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're planning,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but I won't let you use my sister\Nas a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best opportunity to gauge\Nthe Other weapons' power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.83,0:09:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We've confirmed Fubuki Spring's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-Carry out the mission now.\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fubuki, you are Suoh's enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.13,0:09:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't expect you to\Nhide this trick up your sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.33,0:09:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Put them to good use. We can deal\Nsignificant damage to Seiran with these.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Major General Fubuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be OSF soldiers from Suoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We must leave this place together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-Are you all right?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is it okay?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Eliminate these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, get out of there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, can you hear me? Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me, Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:11:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Those people...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Positive ID on Kasane Randall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Commencing brain retrieval.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, we don't want to fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.67,0:12:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,These people are using their allies to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't tell enemies from allies.\NThis is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.25,0:12:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.04,0:13:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.33,0:14:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally understand why I was\Nturned into this form.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so that I can protect you, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Run. I'll distract that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No. even with your Other power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not alone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone else will help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll figure out a solution, so please...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry you're always so worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So let me be the cool Big Sister for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you should come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where can I possibly go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi, I leave Kasane to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.79,0:15:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.42,0:15:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're still recovering,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is too weak even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Suoh is at the end of their rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,To think they actually sent hitmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They are getting impatient.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if you know something useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.50,0:16:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this can't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, you really are a cry baby, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you come back?\NIt's still too dangerous to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad all of you are safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister, it must hurt a lot.\NYou're covered in wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I don't feel any pain anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After I was turned into this thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,after taking medicine made from human brains,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,death is the only thing I seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I get to live like a human
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,despite having the form of Other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kasane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.75,0:17:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Live on for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.83,0:18:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go. Don't leave me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Alice.\N-Karen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.42,0:18:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I fail again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Karen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:18:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rewrite it as many times as it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen copied Kasane's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he copy the Red Strings as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What is his motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he going back in time to save Alice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is no sign\Nof the Red Strings being triggered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That is Arahabaki's access terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like the one we found at Togetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What if it happens again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the risk, but I must do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very similar to OSF's system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.96,0:20:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems we can upload images here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Messages sent from Arahabaki
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,will be forced on all citizens
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,regardless of age and gender,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and against their will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The people will learn about the video file.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,People will start asking\Nwhy they were given this information.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, I want to know
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,how people will react\Nafter learning the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I must pave my own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,DO YOU WISH TO EXECUTE THE ORDER?\NYES OR NO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We inherited the legacy from Yakumo Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We must have our revenge on the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even users like us can't handle\Nthe load from SAS!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.13,0:21:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All we need is their brains and body parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we received the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Communication is cut off in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.75,0:21:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.50,0:21:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,After the people of New Himuka\Nwatch this footage,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be mass protests outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This footage is a catalyst.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.33,0:22:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no way to know about\Nthe future of New Himuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.58,0:22:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know what's going on inside the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.21,0:22:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm troubled by my own yearning♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.42,0:22:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Unveil the blocked sun ray♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's a stranger in me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫That I've never seen♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.96,0:22:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I can not soar in the sky without fear♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.88,0:22:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm spreading my wings♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.04,0:22:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Dancing gracefully like a bird♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.38,0:23:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And gazing towards the scarlet sky♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I chased after the gust♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♫The scenery spreads\Ninto the ever-changing world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Inside the intertwined brilliance♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.92,0:23:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'm still searching for tomorrow's direction♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Tomorrow's in your hands♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don't tell me now you're afraid♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.71,0:23:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫There's no time to waste♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.21,0:23:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Go forward♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.38,0:23:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Have no fear for anything♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.71,0:23:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Now, let's go♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.17,0:23:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Into a brand new day♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.83,0:24:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,ARAHABAKI'S TRAP
